      <li id="ref11"><b>Dense Passage Retrieval for Open-Domain Question Answering.</b> <span class="auth">Karpukhin, Oğuz, Min, Lewis, Wu, Edunov, Chen, Yih (2020).</span> <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2004.04906" target="_blank" rel="noopener">arxiv.org/abs/2004.04906</a></li>
      <li id="ref12"><b>Efficient and Robust Approximate Nearest Neighbor Search using HNSW Graphs.</b> <span class="auth">Malkov, Yashunin (2016/2018).</span> <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.09320" target="_blank" rel="noopener">arxiv.org/abs/1603.09320</a></li>
      <li id="ref13"><b>Retrieval Augmentation Reduces Hallucination in Conversation.</b> <span class="auth">Shuster, Poff, Chen, Kiela, Weston (2021).</span> <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2104.07567" target="_blank" rel="noopener">arxiv.org/abs/2104.07567</a></li>
      <li id="ref14"><b>Recursively Split by Character (RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter).</b> <span class="auth">LangChain Official Documentation.</span> <a href="https://docs.langchain.com/oss/python/integrations/splitters/recursive_text_splitter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">docs.langchain.com — recursive text splitter</a></li>
      <li id="ref15"><b>Introducing Contextual Retrieval.</b> <span class="auth">Anthropic (2024).</span> <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/contextual-retrieval" target="_blank" rel="noopener">anthropic.com/engineering/contextual-retrieval</a></li>
