      <li id="ref19"><b>Tool Use (Anthropic) / Function Calling (OpenAI) — official documentation.</b> <span class="auth">Anthropic &amp; OpenAI.</span> <a href="https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/docs/build-with-claude/tool-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Claude tool use</a> · <a href="https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/function-calling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenAI function calling</a></li>
