      <li id="ref25"><b>Building Effective Agents.</b> <span class="auth">Schluntz, Zhang — Anthropic (2024).</span> <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/building-effective-agents" target="_blank" rel="noopener">anthropic.com/engineering/building-effective-agents</a></li>
